CHANGE LOG
==========


2023-06-06 - v0.33.1
--------------------

### Fixed
    - Interface definition for `OpenTracing::Implementation::Interface::Bootstrap`

### Added
    - convenience method `bootstrap_global-default_tracer`

### Changed
    - PERL_OPENTRACING_IMPLEMENTATION in favour of OPENTRACING_IMPLEMENTATION
    - PERL_OPENTRACING_DEBUG in favour of OPENTRACING_DEBUG plus DEBUG

### Improved
    - tests
    - documentation



2021-11-23 - v0.32.0
--------------------

### Updated
    - use Role::Declare::Should instead of OPENTRACING_INTERFACE to check return


2020-01-15 - v0.31.0
--------------------

### Added
