    - convenience method `bootstrap_default_tracer`

### Updated
    - Documentation about `OPENTRACING_IMPLEMENTATION` env-var


2020-01-15 - v0.03
------------------

### Changed
    - renamed internal required method to `bootstrap_tracer`
    

